description: This Chainlink VRF common Gaston purrs with a rating of 45, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 45, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, Stringalong for East, Box for South, and 5 for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60451-37450-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [45 Votes, Common]
